-- China Vows to Continue Supply of Rare Earths After NYT Reports Export Ban
-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 2010-10-20T04:14:28Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-20/china-vows-to-continue-supply-of-rare-earths-after-nyt-reports-export-ban.html
China’s Commerce Ministry pledged
that the country will “continue to supply rare earths to the
world,” in response to claims in the New York Times that an
informal ban on exports has widened to include Europe and the
U.S.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Yidi Zhao in Beijing at 
 yzhao7@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Ben Richardson at 
 brichardson8@bloomberg.net  